commit message: Add support for both UDP and TLS STUN servers discovered by DNS SRV
Add logic for checking the phone number entered by the user at registration
Add more detail to error when connection fails
TcpSocket: clear lock on exception.  Add more logging.
TcpSocket: improve logging about lock status
TcpSocket: add support for custom root CAs bundled with the app.  Add CAcert.org root.
